<HEADLINE> Weather Forecast for Major World Cities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 24 (Xinhua) -- Weather forecast for 11 major
world cities from 20:00 today to 20:00 on April 25, issued by
China's Central Meteorological Station tonight:
</P>
<P>
Beijing: min. 5 degrees C., max. 24 degrees C., clear, gentle
breeze to calm.
</P>
<P>
Tokyo: min. 18 degrees C., max. 24 degrees C., drizzle, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Bangkok: min. 29 degrees C., max. 36 degrees C., cloudy, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Sydney: min. 15 degrees C., max. 19 degrees C., drizzle, calm
to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Karachi: min. 25 degrees C., max. 34 degrees, cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Cairo: min. 14 degrees C., max. 28 degrees C., clear to cloudy,
calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Moscow: min. 2 degrees C., max. 17 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Frankfurt: min. 10 degrees C., max. 20 degrees C., overcast to
cloudy, calm to gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
Paris: min. 8 degrees C., max. 17 degrees C., cloudy, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
London: min. 7 degrees C., max. 15 degrees C., drizzle, calm to
gentle breeze.
</P>
<P>
New York: min. 8 degrees C., max. 14 degrees C., drizzle, calm
to gentle breeze.  
</P>
</TEXT>
