<HEADLINE> Intertoto Cup to Kick off in June </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
GENEVA, April 24 (Xinhua) -- The Intertoto Cup will run from
June 20 to August 25, UEFA said in Nyon, Switzerland on Friday.
</P>
<P>
In the first round, forty teams will play in the two-leg games
with the 20 winners advancing to the second round together with 12
of the 20 seeded teams.
</P>
<P>
The first round is slated on June 20/21 and June 27/28, and the
second round scheduled on July 4/5 and July 11/12.
</P>
<P>
In the third round, the 16 winners will be joined by eight top
seeds on July 18/19 and July 25.
</P>
<P>
The 12 winners will then compete in the semifinals on July 29
and August 5 before the six winners play for three UEFA Cup places
on August 11 and 25.
</P>
<P>
The eight top seeds are the top teams from Italy, France,
Spain, Germany, Netherlands, Portugal, England and Belgium.
</P>
<P>
No country can enter more than two teams. 
</P>
