guard in a Neufchateau court and started his run with the shotgun
of the police in a stolen car toward the borders of Luxembourg and
France.
</P>
<P>
The Belgian police had to seal off the borders while the French
police did the same on their part. Altogether police in five
countries were mobilized to join the manhunt.
</P>
<P>
Dutroux was accused of killing four of the six young girls he
had abducted in mid 1996 as a nation-wide child sex ring was
exposed and shocked the Belgian public.  
