fell 12.43 to 1,868.96.
</P>
<P>
The Russell 2000 index of smaller companies fell 4.73 to
480.22, and the American Stock Exchange composite index fell 6.19
to 741.86.
</P>
<P>
Disney and Merck fell sharply as the Dow's two biggest
decliners, negating a big gain from Hewlett-Packard, which rallied
after an upbeat assessment by Prudential Securities. 
</P>
