<HEADLINE> Afghan Taliban Launch Offensive North of Kabul </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ISLAMABAD, April 25 (Xinhua) -- The Afghan Islamic Taliban
militia Saturday launched an early morning attack on opposition
troops north of the Afghan capital Kabul but failed to gain any
ground, reports reaching here said.
</P>
