explosion has anything to do with the ethnic conflicts in the
town, which has led to dozens of deaths in recent eruptions of
violence.
</P>
<P>
The explosion in Ile-Ife came barely 24 hours after a huge
explosion killed three persons and injured several others in
Lagos, Wednesday night.
</P>
<P>
Osun State Administrator Lieutenant-Colonel Anthony Obi, who
visited the site, condemned the explosions in strong terms, saying
that they were designed to derail the country's political transition
program. 
