Ukrainian counterpart Valery Pustovoitenko, adding that Austria
also supports Ukrainian entry into the World Trade
Organization. As the presidency state of the EU in the second half
of 1998, Austria would help Ukraine eliminate trade barriers and
improve the investment environment to promote the implementation
of partnership pacts between the EU and Ukraine, said Klima.
(Ukraine-Austria-EU) 
</P>
