Commission Bureau of the Tigray Region announced that the new
stadium which will be built in Mekelle will cost fifty million
Birr (about 7.2 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The bureau said, the construction work is expected to begin
next year and when completed, it will be the biggest stadium in
Ethiopia.
</P>
<P>
Addis Ababa Stadium has a 35,000 to 40,000 seating capacity.
</P>
